      "1": "Simon Peter|strong=\"G4074\", servant|strong=\"G1401\"and|strong=\"G2532\"apostle|strong=\"G0652\"of|strong=\"G2316\"Jesus|strong=\"G2424\"Christ|strong=\"G5547\", to|strong=\"G2532\"them|strong=\"G1722\"that|strong=\"G2316\"have|strong=\"G2532\"obtained equal faith|strong=\"G4102\"with|strong=\"G1722\"us|strong=\"G1722\"in|strong=\"G1722\"the|strong=\"G3588\"justice|strong=\"G1343\"of|strong=\"G2316\"our|strong=\"G2316\"God|strong=\"G2316\"and|strong=\"G2532\"Saviour Jesus|strong=\"G2424\"Christ|strong=\"G5547\".",
