      "1": "But|strong=\"G1161\"there|strong=\"G1510\"were|strong=\"G1510\"also|strong=\"G2532\"false|strong=\"G5578\"prophets|strong=\"G5578\"among|strong=\"G1722\"the|strong=\"G3588\"people|strong=\"G2992\", even|strong=\"G2532\"as|strong=\"G5613\"there|strong=\"G1510\"shall|strong=\"G2532\"be|strong=\"G1510\"among|strong=\"G1722\"you|strong=\"G5210\"lying teachers|strong=\"G5572\", who|strong=\"G3588\"shall|strong=\"G2532\"bring|strong=\"G1863\"in|strong=\"G1722\"sects of|strong=\"G1722\"perdition|strong=\"G0684\", and|strong=\"G2532\"deny|strong=\"G0720\"the|strong=\"G3588\"Lord|strong=\"G1203\"who|strong=\"G3588\"bought|strong=\"G0059\"them|strong=\"G0846\": bringing|strong=\"G1863\"upon|strong=\"G1510\"themselves|strong=\"G1438\"swift|strong=\"G5031\"destruction|strong=\"G0684\".",
