      "20": "For|strong=\"G1063\"if|strong=\"G1487\", flying from|strong=\"G1722\"the|strong=\"G3588\"pollutions of|strong=\"G2962\"the|strong=\"G3588\"world|strong=\"G2889\", through|strong=\"G1722\"the|strong=\"G3588\"knowledge|strong=\"G1922\"of|strong=\"G2962\"our|strong=\"G2424\"Lord|strong=\"G2962\"and|strong=\"G2532\"Saviour Jesus|strong=\"G2424\"Christ|strong=\"G5547\", they|strong=\"G0846\"be|strong=\"G1096\"again|strong=\"G3825\"entangled|strong=\"G1707\"in|strong=\"G1722\"them|strong=\"G0846\"and|strong=\"G2532\"overcome|strong=\"G2274\": their|strong=\"G0846\"latter state is|strong=\"G3778\"become|strong=\"G1096\"unto them|strong=\"G0846\"worse|strong=\"G5501\"than|strong=\"G2532\"the|strong=\"G3588\"former.",
